jim bittermann cnn's senior international correspondent based paris. since joining cnn 1996, covered death princess diana 1997, nato air strikes kosovo 1998, earthquake turkey 1999 world cup soccer championships, among stories. full bio jim bittermann cnn's senior international correspondent based paris. since joining cnn 1996, covered death princess diana 1997, nato air strikes kosovo 1998, earthquake turkey 1999 world cup soccer championships, among stories. bittermann joined cnn abc news, paris news correspondent 1990-1996. years abc, covered wide range international events, including dissolution soviet union, gulf war middle east peace process u.s. deployment somalia. long-form projects abc included betrayed blood, report french aids-tainted blood scandal primetime live two half-hour special reports nightline ted koppel, perfect messiah fashion conspiracy. 1978-1990, bittermann european correspondent nbc news. based rome 1978-1979, covered two papal transitions travels pope john paul ii. 1980-1990, based paris. there, reported many decade's major international stories eastern europe, northern western africa, middle east, philippines, japan soviet union. received national news emmy award coverage 1988 sudan famine. prior nbc, bittermann toronto-based correspondent producer canadian broadcasting corp.'s newsmagazine. also worked reporter wkyc-tv cleveland, ohio, 1973-1975 working one year wqed-tv, public television station pittsburgh. 1971-1972, bittermann traveled national presidential campaign staffs sen. birch bayh indiana sen. edmund muskie maine. began career broadcast journalism 1970 wtmj-tv milwaukee, one year newspaper reporter waukegan news-sun waukegan, ill. many honors include cableace award cnn's coverage civil war zaire. panel moderator world economic forum davos, switzerland, member jury french film competition les lumieres de paris. since 1998, bittermann assistant adjunct professor communication american university paris, teaching courses broadcast news documentary film, among subjects. bittermann earned bachelor's degree southern illinois university, 1989 named southern illinois university's journalism alumnus year. 2000 received university's alumni achievement award.
